Patent Applications

Four provisional patent applications covering Cognograph's spatial AI
innovations were filed with the United States Patent and Trademark Office
in February 2026. The applications cover:

1. Graph-based automatic context assembly in AI conversation interfaces
2. Spatial topology-based agent permission and orchestration control
3. Position-based trigger activation in spatial computing interfaces
4. Conversational plan refinement with preview and atomic execution
